</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "0" border-bottom = "0" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Poškodený ventilátor chladiča.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "0" border-bottom = "0" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Vyčistite kondenzátor.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "0" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Chybná činnosť ventilátora chladiča.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "0" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Skontrolujte a opravte ventilátor chladiča.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Vysoký tlak v oboch ukazovateľoch, vysokotlakovom aj nízkotlakovom.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Trubica nízkotlakovej časti nie je na dotyk studená.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Vzduch v klimatizačnom systéme
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(nesprávne vypustenie).
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Vymeňte kondenzátor.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Skontrolujte množstvo kompresorového oleja, ako aj to, či sa v ňom nenachádzajú znečisťujúce prímesi.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Odčerpajte zo systému chladiacu kvapalinu a naplňte ho novou.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
450 – 550 (4,6 – 5,6) (65,3 – 79,8)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Vysoký tlak v oboch ukazovateľoch, vysokotlakovom aj nízkotlakovom.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Veľké množstvo námrazy alebo rosy na trubici nízkotlakovej časti.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Porucha expanzného ventilu.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Tok chladiacej kvapaliny nie je správne regulovaný.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
